race.comment: SATISFIED MUGS (1) returns from a break of four months. Consistent performer last prep whose most recent appearance resulted in a fifth over 1000m at Townsville. Rates highly and a bold showing is expected. DRAGON TALES (2) made it two wins on the bounce last start when he scored by 0.6 lengths over 1000m at Home Hill. Taking on a better field but he is good enough to figure in the finish. GEM OF SCOTS (4) is a promising type who scored at her last run before a break four months ago over 950m at this track. Has to be included. NORDIC INVADER (3) last appeared when he got the cash over 1200m at Townsville on September 9. Among the better hopes.
